author: Feuerborn, Justus, 1587-1656
title: Disputatio theologica quâ ex Dei verbo explicatur quæstio: an in infantes cadant peccata actualia? & analogæ quæstiones concurrentes simul evolvuntur cujus subiecta themata ... sub præsidio Justi Fewrbornii ... respondendo defendet publicè Richardus Benni
